column2: Volume-to-weight calculator by Martin Lersch (v.2, January 2014)
Convert US customary units to grams based on densities
Amount
*) Allowed units:
US volume units: t, T, floz, c, pt, qt, gal
US weight units: oz, lb
Metric volume units: ml, dl, l
Metric weight units: g, kg
For eggs, egg whites, egg yolks and stick of butter unit field is left blank
Navigation
Use tab or left/right arrow to navigate in/out of ingredients
Autocomplete feature in ingredient field requires macros to be enabled
Use up/down arrows to navigate up/down in drop down list of ingredients
References
Densities mainly taken from rec.food.cooking and USDA National Nutrient Database
Some additional data from http://www.aqua-calc.com
Some densities added/corrected by Martin Lersch
